########### Ghidra Integration Plugin #############################

Flag ida
  Description: Build Ghidra integration plugin
  Default: false

Library bap_ghidra_plugin
  Build$:           flag(everything) || flag(ghidra)
  Path:             plugins/ghidra
  FindlibName:      bap-plugin-ghidra
  CompiledObject:   best
  BuildDepends:     bap, core_kernel, ppx_jane, fileutils,
                    bap-knowledge, regular, bap-future, bap-main
  Modules:          Ghidra_main
  InternalModules:  Bap_ghidra_config
  XMETADescription: uses Ghidra to provide rooter, symbolizer, and reconstructor
  XMETAExtraLines:  tags="ghidra, rooter, brancher, symbolizer, reconstructor"
